ke stupid people famous."},{"pid":"2a942b86b885f5b85bdb9fc934b4fd0877fdfa61","tid":1629220,"uid":199768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"博出位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4fe5ddd847057c762c2347ebca91e4dd1133cc","tid":1629220,"uid":6219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"佢幾時生乳癌死"},{"pid":"bccf313e374c3a559d12573aad0e3c6bbed31c74","tid":1629220,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:41:32.000Z","msg":"而家開始推啲藝人出嚟受靶<br />\n一開波搵極端豬扒<br />\n後面一定會有啲靚嘅或者人氣高嘅出嚟交喊戲㗎啦<br />\n你哋又陪佢哋玩咁開心嘅"}]}